long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Control your online privacy with easy-to-use web search experience. Download the free extension today!

Iolo SafeSearch powered by OneSearch prioritizes your privacy. Search profiling and ad-targeting are things of the past as you find what you’re searching for quickly and easily. SafeSearch also encrypts your search terms for extra security. Benefits include:

Personal privacy: search for personal topics without being cookied or tracked.

No algorithm bias –Your search term habits and data are private so they can’t be used to filter search results.
